It'd be nice if you either marked this as deprecated or actually updated it to reflect the current practices for creating cert-manager resources
Otherwise, people are going to find your article, attempt to follow it, and then have to tear down their cluster when the various hanging resources created by the old cert-manager manifests don't disappear properly.
I know, because I just had to do this on a brand-new k3s install.
